# Disposable Exec Architecture

Disposable Exec is a lightweight sandbox runtime for executing
AI-generated Python code safely.

The system consists of three components:

1. SDK (client)
2. Execution API server
3. Isolated runtime

Architecture flow:

AI Agent
   │
   │ SDK call
   ▼
Disposable Client
   │
   │ HTTP request
   ▼
Disposable Server
   │
   │ spawn sandbox
   ▼
Disposable Runtime
   │
   │ execute python code
   ▼
Result (stdout / stderr / exit_code)

Example flow:

Agent → SDK.run() → HTTP /run → sandbox execution → return result